DEPRECATED: This file has been replaced by ai_conversation module's AIApiService.

The agent_evaluation module now uses '@ai_conversation.ai_api_service' for all
AI API functionality instead of maintaining its own duplicate implementation.

In agent_evaluation.services.yml, the service 'agent_evaluation.api_service' 
is now an alias to 'ai_conversation.ai_api_service'.

To migrate your code:
- Replace: \Drupal::service('agent_evaluation.api_service')
- With: \Drupal::service('ai_conversation.ai_api_service')

- Replace: use Drupal\agent_evaluation\Service\AIApiService;
- With: use Drupal\ai_conversation\Service\AIApiServiceInterface;

Date deprecated: February 11, 2026
To remove: After verifying all code uses ai_conversation service

Related Changes:
- Removed duplicate AIConversationSettingsForm - use ai_conversation form instead
- Removed duplicate routing for /admin/config/ai-conversation/settings  
- ChatController now injects ai_conversation.ai_api_service
- SettingsForm now uses ai_conversation.ai_api_service
